graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Notebook Controller Component"
        Controller[OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>Controller]
        Webhook[NotebookWebhook<br/>MutatingWebhook]
        Manager[Manager Deployment<br/>Port 8080/8081/8443]

        Controller -->|handles webhook| Webhook
        Manager -->|hosts| Controller
        Manager -->|hosts| Webhook
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| Controller
    NotebookCR -->|mutated by| Webhook

    subgraph "Created Resources (OAuth Enabled)"
        SA["ServiceAccount<br/>(notebook-name)-sa"]
        Service["Service<br/>(notebook-name)-tls<br/>443:8443/TCP"]
        Secret1["Secret<br/>(notebook-name)-oauth-config"]
        Secret2["Secret<br/>(notebook-name)-tls"]
        Route["OpenShift Route<br/>(notebook-name)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
        NP1["NetworkPolicy<br/>(notebook-name)-ctrl-np"]
        NP2["NetworkPolicy<br/>(notebook-name)-oauth-np"]
        CM["ConfigMap<br/>workbench-trusted-ca-bundle"]
    end

    Controller -->|creates| SA
    Controller -->|creates| Service
    Controller -->|creates| Secret1
    Controller -->|creates| Secret2
    Controller -->|creates| Route
    Controller -->|creates| NP1
    Controller -->|creates| NP2
    Controller -->|creates/merges| CM

    subgraph "Notebook Pod (with OAuth)"
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>Port 8443/TCP HTTPS]
        NotebookContainer[Notebook Container<br/>Port 8888/TCP HTTP]

        OAuthProxy -->|proxies to| NotebookContainer
    end

    Webhook -->|injects| OAuthProxy
    Route -->|routes to| Service
    Service -->|targets| OAuthProxy

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        KubeAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        OSRouter[OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        OSOAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        ImageStream[ImageStream API<br/>OpenShift]
        ServiceCA[Service CA<br/>Cert Provisioning]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/creates resources| KubeAPI
    Webhook -->|resolves images| ImageStream
    Route -->|handled by| OSRouter
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OSOAuth
    Service -->|cert via annotation| ServiceCA

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller<br/>Creates StatefulSet]
        ODHOperator[ODH Operator<br/>Provides CA Bundle]
        ODHTrustedCA[ConfigMap<br/>odh-trusted-ca-bundle]
    end

    NotebookCR -->|also watched by| KubeflowController
    Controller -->|watches| ODHTrustedCA
    ODHOperator -->|manages| ODHTrustedCA

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Manager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookContainer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KubeAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSRouter fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSOAuth fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ImageStream fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceCA fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KubeflowController fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ODHOperator fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
